net.edudb.operator.parameter

Interface OperatorParameter

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExpressionTree, Relation, Table
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryExpressionTree, BinaryTable, Expression, InsertOperatorParameter, ProjectOperatorParameter, RelationOperatorParameter, SQLCreateTableStatement, SQLDeleteStatement, SQLInsertStatement, SQLSelectStatement, SQLStatement, SQLUpdateStatement, UpdateTableOperatorParameter, VolatileRelation

    public interface OperatorParameter
    A marker interface. An OperatorParameter is additional information that a relational algebra operator can have other than its type and children.
    Author:
    Ahmed Abdul Badie
